th LeBron Jamesduring the opening ceremony, becoming the first American tennis player to earn the honor.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9967982877981436, \"rank\": 0.002259863070447319, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This definitely will not be the only time tennis fans see Gauff at an Olympics.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will very likely compete in the 2028 Games in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999131435209841, \"rank\": 8.48799070033599e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Madison Williams is a staff writer on the Breaking and Trending News team at Sports Illustrated, where she specializes in tennis but covers a wide range of sports from a national perspective.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"score\": 0.9999999985600425, \"rank\": 1.439942686007429e-09, \"text\": \"Madison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\"}, {\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 0.9999999956662577, \"rank\